title: NEVER STOP 2 REST - A Definitive Weightlifting Song Compilation
description: This is the elite and explicit collection of songs for weightlifting, running, sports-training, etc. created by Nathan Smith. It is designed to be played on shuffle for an effective 2 hour and 35 minute adrenaline rush. It also includes a 3 minute warm up song: A Cold Day in the Sun. A full list of these songs can be found at http://music.qualityliquidationsales.com/ for sampling.
